{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC10_MER_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x25,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "That's..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I wonder what it is...<CR>I don't know, but...it's so cute!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, it's Homunculus. He's as cute as ever...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Oh, it went inside Marietta's store..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x214,
            "name_id": 0x2b,
            "extra_id": 0x220,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I looking for pretty sparkles.<CR>You have here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Pretty sparkles...?<CR>I wonder what those are..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x214,
            "name_id": 0x2b,
            "extra_id": 0x220,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Sparkles. They look pretty like stars and melt. Sparkles."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Pretty like stars...? Are they like jewels? They're gonna be pretty pricy then."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x214,
            "name_id": 0x2b,
            "extra_id": 0x220,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I have money. Lots of it.<CR>I buy them all. Don't worry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x12d,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Whoa, this much...? I can see you're looking for considerably high-priced items."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x214,
            "name_id": 0x2b,
            "extra_id": 0x220,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Can I buy sparkles with this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x12b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "It might be hard for me to procure them right away, but with this much money..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x1a6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure I'll be able to provide you with items that'll measure up to your wishes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x214,
            "name_id": 0x2b,
            "extra_id": 0x227,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Not measure. Sparkles!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Oh, right, right.<CR>Umm, about the deadline..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x214,
            "name_id": 0x2b,
            "extra_id": 0x22a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Deadline? What's that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Umm, a deadline is, well, basically..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Wait 30 days. Lovely sparkles, delivered to you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x214,
            "name_id": 0x2b,
            "extra_id": 0x220,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Okay. Wait 30 days. I count on you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "That was a reeeally cute customer."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "He was cute, but dealing with him made me nervous. Non-human customers are very rare..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "And it's also rare for a Homunculus<CR>to come to town. Well, whoever the<CR>customer is doesn't matter."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "He paid a lot in advance, so I need to get items that meet his demand!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "But just having \"sparkles\" as a hint is hard..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x7a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "This is where I show off what a merchant can do. Hmhm, I've been itching to put my skills to good use."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I feel a slight tinge of uneasiness for some reason..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "It seemed like he wanted jewels,<CR>but I wonder if Homunculi know<CR>the value of them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x7c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "That's not the problem here...<CR>Wait, I mean...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Owner, if you were watching,<CR>you should've helped me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x141,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "N-No. I feel like I'm not very good at dealing with them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x143,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "It's hard to grasp what someone wants when I can't understand how their minds work."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, it might not be necessary to take everything they say seriously..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Whoever the customer is, they're still a customer. It's my duty as a merchant to respond to them sincerely."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Y-Yup, that's correct. It's just as you say."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1a0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "With that being said, I leave this case entirely to you. Good luck."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x79,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Of course... Leave it to me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x7b,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, it's the biggest job we've had in a while. All right, I need to do this!"
        }
    ]
}